        <section name="Welcome to AS3commons logging">
             AS3commons-logging is an open-source library providing an abstraction over 
             logging framework implementations. Being a pure actionscript library it can 
             be used for any Flash/Flex/AIR project.
        </section>
        
        <section name="Download">
             <a href="http://projects.yoolab.org/maven/content/repositories/releases/org/as3commons/as3commons-logging/2.5.1/as3commons-logging-2.5.1.swc">
